%% Auth Sequence - Mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant Browser
  participant Frontend
  participant Backend
  participant DB

  Browser->>Frontend: submit signup form
  Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/auth/register
  Backend->>DB: create user
  DB-->>Backend: user created
  Backend-->>Frontend: set cookie / return user
  Frontend-->>Browser: update UI, store in Redux
